The goal of this assignment is to review a six sigma case study to illustrate the methodology further and illustrate how organizations have used the Six Sigma methodology to improve their performance. 

Review criteria
less 
This assignment is a practice assignment that will not count toward your final grade. While I encourage you to take this seriously, when submitting and reviewing, this will not impact your grade in the course.

Step-By-Step Assignment Instructions
less 
Assignment Topic: Six Sigma Cases
https://www.benchmarksixsigma.com/lean-six-sigma-case-studies/category/lean-six-sigma-case-studies/green-belt-qualified/
You can choose from the following cases that are listed at Benchmark Six Sigma.â€‹ Be sure to click through to the full project at the bottom.

Setup instructions:

Before you begin, you will need to thoroughly read the case study. I would like you to think about the following questions:

What issue did the organization face and why did it need to be addressed?

How did they show that there was a problem?

What analysis did they perform and what did that analysis indicate?

How did they address the problems?

What did they do to ensure the problem did not reemerge? 

How to submit:

For each of the questions above, please prepare a short answer with examples from the case. The answer to each question should not be longer than 250 words.

